Amal movement on Saturday night in south Lebanon, Lebanese police
said on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
It is the first conflict between the two Shiite organizations,
which have fought against the Israeli occupation side by side,
since Israel withdrew its troops from south Lebanon on May 24.
(Lebanon-Militia Clash)
</P>
