problem of the Angolan civil war, stressing that "peace is an
essential condition towards development".
</P>
<P>
Sampaio also welcomed the announcement of the 2001 elections
made by Angolan President Jose Eduardo dos Santos in early this
year.
</P>
<P>
He said: "I rejoice at the announcement made by the Angolan
president on the holding of democratic elections in 2001", and
asked Angolan Parliament Speaker Roberto de Almeida, who is
representing dos Santos at the summit, to convey the message to
the Angolan president. 
